      &lt;img alt="" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/SNP-bpbztMheYeU1Yj60Fw0Q2vg=/100x0:1180x720/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/69133843/re_village_jan21_screens_creature_01_1611268587718.0.jpg" /&gt;
