    <title>Arcade Fire released an epic 45-minute single — in Headspace’s meditation app</title>
    <content type="html">  

    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img alt="2018 Life Is Beautiful Festival - Day 3" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/UT8NRn0mD5SlQLaPw6TWaoPBMAc=/0x39:3000x2039/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/69132982/1039320710.0.jpg" /&gt;
        &lt;figcaption&gt;Photo by Tim Mosenfelder/Getty Images&lt;/figcaption&gt;
    &lt;/figure&gt;

  &lt;p id="pdwbRQ"&gt;Arcade Fire has a new single out — sort of. The Canadian indie rock band has released a new 45-minute instrumental composition called “Memories In The Age Of Anxiety,” but the new song is actually a collaboration with meditation app Headspace, and you can only listen to it there.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p id="QCudSP"&gt;The new track was created in collaboration with John Legend and, as &lt;a href="https://www.stereogum.com/2144197/arcade-fire-release-new-45-minute-song-for-meditation-app/music/"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Stereogum&lt;/em&gt; notes&lt;/a&gt;, is one of the first new pieces of music from the group since its cover of “&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qpYOstfcQBs"&gt;Baby Mine&lt;/a&gt;” in the 2019 live-action version of &lt;em&gt;Dumbo.&lt;/em&gt; (It’s the band’s first original song since its 2017 studio album &lt;em&gt;Everything Now.&lt;/em&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div id="Wwmda5"&gt;
&lt;blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned="" data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CNpvCckJY00/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="13" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"&gt;&lt;div style="padding:16px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CNpvCckJY00/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;amp;utm_campaign=loading" style=" background:#FFFFFF; line-height:0; padding:0 0; text-align:center; text-decoration:none; width:100%;" target="_blank"&gt; &lt;div style=" display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center;"&gt; &lt;div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"&gt; &lt;div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
